Class IloCplex.SolutionSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.SolutionSource
  • Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static final class IloCplex.SolutionSource
extends java.lang.Object

    This enumeration lists the values that tell for which type of solution the incumbent callback or lazy constraint callback was invoked.

    • NodeSolution
    • HeuristicSolution
    • UserSolution

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int HeuristicSolution
      The integral solution was found by a CPLEX internal heuristic.
      static int NodeSolution
      The integral solution was found as the solution to an LP-relaxation of a node in the search tree.
      static int UserSolution
      The integral solution was found by the user's heuristic callback function.
